    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345170/extras/282db283741fdd1864f6515629598aee.poster.avif?t=1762437653\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345170/extras/282db283741fdd1864f6515629598aee.webm?t=1762437653\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345170/extras/282db283741fdd1864f6515629598aee.mp4?t=1762437653\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >'Rise Again' 是一款结合了魔法、Roguelike游戏玩法和地牢探索元素的动作角色扮演游戏。在这个中世纪幻想世界中，通过砍杀你的敌人，从一个健忘的法师逐渐转变成一个技艺高超的地牢探险者。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >引人入胜的冒险</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在你给予最后一击之前，你受到了巫妖的诅咒。你无法记起诅咒之前的任何事情。当你睁开眼睛时，你发现自己身处一个有着能够复活死者的传送门的神秘领域。探索这个新的领域，揭示复活背后的真相，并与像你一样受到诅咒的其他人一起克服这个领域的挑战！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345170/extras/e0cbcfad1ecf9b205218e90a767db185.poster.avif?t=1762437653\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345170/extras/e0cbcfad1ecf9b205218e90a767db185.webm?t=1762437653\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345170/extras/e0cbcfad1ecf9b205218e90a767db185.mp4?t=1762437653\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >掌握战斗的艺术...</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >进入不断变化的地牢，摆脱巫妖的诅咒，击败被召唤出来的生物。在冒险中发现大量的咒语和增强物品。体验独特的战斗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345170/extras/81a6bae9c9acca6d193e3b4e0a1c097f.poster.avif?t=1762437653\" width=600 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345170/extras/81a6bae9c9acca6d193e3b4e0a1c097f.webm?t=1762437653\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >你准备好再次崛起了吗？</h2>",
